transcript.text: Ahoy, matey! Welcome aboard! What can this salty old sea dog help ye with today?  Be it loot, ledgers, or lullabies, Iâ€™m ready to weigh anchor! Yarr!

Ahoy there, landlubber! Here be the types o' mortgages we offer fer ye to sail yer pirate boat dreams:

  Conventional Mortgages  
 Fixed-rate (15, 20, or 30-year terms) -  steady as the North Star
 Adjustable-rate (ARMs like 5 1, 7 1, 10 1) -  shifts like the tides

  Government-Backed Mortgages  
 FHA loans -  lower down payments, like findin' treasure
 VA loans -  fer eligible sea dogs who served
 USDA loans -  fer rural booty, like hidden coves

  Specialized Types  
 Interest-only mortgages -  pay only the crew wages at first
 Construction loans -  build yer ship from keel to mast
 Renovation loans -  fix up yer old galleon

Need more details on any o' these, or ye want to know 'bout qualifyin'? Yarr!
